---
title: Beef Steak, Smoked Cheddar & Mushroom Subs with Cos Salad & Dijon Mayonnaise
description: Here’s a delicious, decadent and devilishly fast beef steak sub. We can’t recommend the tender beef enough, it’s mouth-watering with mushrooms and a smokey Cheddar on top. The hint of saucy sweetness comes from the onion chutney tossed through the mushrooms. It will be love at first bite.
